{"tid":1244821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NOW: 本台發現部分速龍小隊近日行動曾在胸口掛上警員編號","createTime":"2019-06-20T05:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T11:17:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f4647b813c64d1819bcd1692bdbb19af480406ca","tid":1244821,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/POLICE-SUIT-190620-12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FPOLICE-SUIT-190620-12.jpg&h=ef824727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NYzMWl3CSVk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNYzMWl3CSVk&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=ee36101e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NYzMWl3CSVk</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】保安局局長李家超指，速龍小隊工作服沒有位置展示警員編號，但本台翻查影片後發現，部分速龍小隊在近日行動中曾經在胸口掛上警員編號。有監警會前委員認為，即使市民未能識別速龍小隊的警員編號，亦可以投訴。<br />\n<br />\n在612衝突中，警方多次出動俗稱「速龍小隊」的特別戰術小隊驅散人群。<br />\n<br />\n全黑制服，配備防毒面罩及頭盔，身上無警員編號，被質疑難以辨認他們的身分作投訴。<br />\n<br />\n李家超昨日指，速龍小隊工作服沒有位置展示警員編號，但是否屬實呢?<br />\n<br />\n本台翻看612衝突前三日，民陣百萬人遊行後有人衝擊立法會，警方出動速龍小隊，多於一名警員胸口前掛上警員編號，亦有些掛上警員職級，部分速龍小隊則只穿上寫有「警察」字樣的制服。<br />\n<br />\n再看星期一，即6月17日，速龍小隊清理龍和道障礙物，部分警員身上掛上警員編號。<br />\n<br />\n有監警會前委員認為，即使速龍小隊制服上無編號仍可以投訴。<br />\n<br />\n警方五年前成立特別戰術小隊，在多次大型群眾活動，包括16年農曆年旺角衝突都有出動，舊制服上肩膊位置印上警員編號。"},{"pid":"3393486c25c89b34d5fe36f79ccd3e4dedb760d5","tid":1244821,"uid":40356,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"今次點兜呢？？"},{"pid":"eb174705a31ccc4c0a5c8cb6aeef722108c6fc81","tid":1244821,"uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:40:54.000Z","msg":"6月9有,6月17有,點解6月12無"},{"pid":"da47c740be643cf678f817902673d2cb4634fe2e","tid":1244821,"uid":186926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:42:27.000Z","msg":"睇下你地仲可以交到幾多次波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328b26e8fe86d24108c8e3967ebe81db6ab41f56","tid":1244821,"uid":12824,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6a80bdbfad5636deb1aa41a339ec7267c1f541","tid":1244821,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:45:18.000Z","msg":"好醜陋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67478f2d24971ef65f48b657fe67250c68586b47","tid":1244821,"uid":221265,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3393486c25c89b34d5fe36f79ccd3e4dedb760d5","tid":1244821,"uid":40356,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"今次點兜呢？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:46:11.000Z","msg":"佢無打算兜<br />\n<br />\n根本唔在乎個個知佢講大話"},{"pid":"5a41e13d8757671902c9cf98bf20a3e3f733f85a","tid":1244821,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9c78941bd16d2ae8f9c179ff2758565bbb3248bc","tid":1244821,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:46:59.000Z","msg":"只系故意除落黎<br />\n避免被投訴都情有可原<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果系無證警員/黑工<br />\ne.g. 引入中國警務人員<br />\n咁成件事就變得好恐怖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6523a1b41651413502b94a661a39e56f2e840229","tid":1244821,"uid":52621,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:47:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n還警員公道<br />\n追究濫權警員</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"40891ffb3378723c360d78947bb39d9e4908940c","tid":1